START

Declare income as double
Declare taxWithholding as double
Declare taxRate as double

Prompt user to enter weekly income
Read income

IF income < 500
    Set taxRate to 0.10
ELSE IF income is between 500 and 1500
    Set taxRate to 0.15
ELSE IF income is between 1500 and 2500
    Set taxRate to 0.20
ELSE
    Set taxRate to 0.30

Calculate taxWithholding = income × taxRate

Display taxWithholding

END
